work_voice: HA! Caught you, fool!
work_voice: Uh, I mean...welcome, new employee!
work_voice: Thank you for joining our team! We're sure you will be an excellent addition to our workplace family.
work_voice: Please remember that one of our conerstone values at this company is TRUST.[pause=.5] That is,[pause=.3] we trust that, during your time here, you will always be on time,[pause=.5] never get sick,[pause=.5] and won't make any escape attempts.
work_voice: Understood? Good!
work_voice: I'll now show you to your living quarters. Follow me, please.
[signal arg="lift_elevator"]
